OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will give her
OL,7,Flong-awaited Spring Statement to
OL,8,FParliament on Wednesday, as she lays
OL,9,Fout her latest plans for the public
OL,10,Ffinances.
OL,12,FThe statement was meant to be an
OL,13,F"update" from the chancellor rather
OL,14,Fthan a full-on fiscal event, but for a
OL,15,Ffew different reasons it's become a
OL,16,Flot more important.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
