OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FA difficult economic climate combined
OL,7,Fwith the fact that Reeves didn't leave
OL,8,Fherself much wriggle room in her
OL,9,FAutumn Budget means she is now
OL,10,Fexpected to set out significant cuts
OL,11,Fon Wednesday.
OL,13,FWhat is the Spring Statement? Is it a
OL,14,FBudget?
OL,16,FRachel Reeves will stand up in the
OL,17,FHouse of Commons on Wednesday and
OL,18,Fdeliver her Spring Statement - in
OL,19,Fpretty much the same way she did at
OL,20,Fthe Budget in October.
