OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FThe speech will be shorter than a
OL,7,FBudget speech, lasting around half an
OL,8,Fhour.
OL,10,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,11,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,12,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,13,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,15,FAlongside the chancellor's statement,
OL,16,Fwe will also get the growth forecast
OL,17,Ffrom the Office for Budget
OL,18,FResponsibility (OBR). The OBR is the
OL,19,Fgovernment's official independent
OL,20,Feconomic forecaster.
