OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FIn her Budget last October, Reeves
OL,7,Fsaid there would only be one major
OL,8,Ffiscal event each year, with the
OL,9,FSpring Statement just acting as an
OL,10,F"update" without any policy changes.
OL,12,FBut while the chancellor insists the
OL,13,FSpring Statement "is not a Budget." a
OL,14,Fnumber of factors mean she's likely to
OL,15,Fmake some significant spending cuts.
OL,16,FThe whole thing hinges on her self-
OL,17,Fimposed fiscal rules, which she is
OL,18,Ffiercely committed to sticking by.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
