OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FGovernments always set themselves
OL,7,Ffiscal rules which they sometimes
OL,8,Fstick by and sometimes don't, but
OL,9,Fafter a period of economic
OL,10,Finstability, Reeves has made them the
OL,11,Ffoundation of her decision-making.
OL,13,FShe wants to prove that Labour can be
OL,14,Ftrusted with the public finances, and
OL,15,Fthat she can bring stability to the
OL,16,Feconomy after the kind of turbulence
OL,17,Fwe say in the the disastrous Truss
OL,18,Fmini-Budget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
