OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FIn their manifesto Labour said they
OL,7,Fwould "strengthen the role of the
OL,8,FOBR," promising in government they
OL,9,Fwould "never sideline the OBR for
OL,10,Fpolitical convenience".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"Every fiscal event making significant
OL,18,Fchanges to taxation or spending will
OL,19,Fbe subject to an independent OBR
OL,20,Fforecast," the manifesto said.
