OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FReeves Budget last Autumn was the
OL,7,Fbiggest tax-raising fiscal event in
OL,8,Fmore than 30 years, as she hiked taxes
OL,9,Fby #40 billion.
OL,11,FAmong the rises were a hike to
OL,12,Femployer national insurance
OL,13,Fcontributions, capital gains tax, and
OL,14,Fapplying VAT to private school fees.
