OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FThe key thing Reeves is expected to
OL,7,Flay out on Wednesday is cuts to
OL,8,Fdepartmental spending. The scale of
OL,9,Fthose cuts isn't yet clear, but there
OL,10,Fhave been reports they could be as
OL,11,Fmuch at 7% in some departments over
OL,12,Fthe next four years.
OL,14,FWe're likely to get the full detail on
OL,15,Fexactly what will be cut in the
OL,16,FSpending Review in June, which will
OL,17,Fset out departmental budgets for 2026-
OL,18,F2027 and 2028-2029.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
