OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FLast week the government announced
OL,7,Fhuge cuts to the benefits system,
OL,8,Fsaying they would save #5 billion by
OL,9,F2030. On Wednesday one of the most
OL,10,Fimportant things to look out for is
OL,11,Fthe government's impact assessment on
OL,12,Fhow many people will be affected by
OL,13,Fthe cuts.
OL,15,FThe OBR will also publish their own
OL,16,Fassessment of the cuts to the benefits
OL,17,Fbill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
