OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FThere's also been lots of discussion
OL,7,Faround whether the Chancellor will
OL,8,Fextend the freeze on income tax
OL,9,Fthresholds, which is due to end in
OL,10,FApril 2028. Keeping the thresholds
OL,11,Ffrozen would drag more people into
OL,12,Fhigher tax brackets, meaning they pay
OL,13,Fmore income tax.
OL,15,FLast month Sir Keir Starmer revealed
OL,16,Fthe government was cutting overseas
OL,17,Faid funding in order pay for an
OL,18,Fincrease in defence spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
