OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FStarmer committed to boost defence
OL,7,Fspending to 2.5% of national income by
OL,8,F2030, after Donald Trump's
OL,9,Fintervention in the Ukraine war raised
OL,10,Ffears a deal with Russia could leave
OL,11,FEurope vulnerable.
OL,13,FOverseas aid will be cut from 0.5% of
