OL,3,CWhat is the Spring Statement and why
OL,4,Cdoes it matter?
OL,6,FShowing the scale of the departmental
OL,7,Fcuts on the table, the Times newspaper
OL,8,Freported on Monday the education
OL,9,Fsecretary has suggested ending
OL,10,Funiversal free school meals for
OL,11,Finfants, and axing free period
OL,12,Fproducts as well as dance, music and
OL,13,FPE schemes.
OL,15,FAsked about those reports on Monday,
OL,16,FReeves said she does not "recognise"
OL,17,Fthem.
